title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Micheletti/de St. Aubin/Birk
description: PA is out, Nordo is in! Pat Micheletti stops by in studio to talk hockey, MNUFC color commentator Kyndra de St. Aubin talks soccer, and Matt Birk makes his regular appearance!
